Class Wall

java.lang.Object
  rampancy.ForcePoint
      rampancy.Wall

public class Wall
extends ForcePoint

The Wall class is a subclass of ForcePoint. It provides a repulsive force that keeps Durandal away from walls.

Author:
Matthew Chun-Lum
